buyGood

public int buyGood(java.lang.String g)
This method check if city market fulfills requirements for use of good and enough money to buy it. If it passes the check corresponding changes are done to the inventory of the market (increase queantity of this good).

Parameters:
g - good to by bought
Returns:
nonzero number if city market had required tech level for use of good and enough money to buy it, else return 0.

buyGood

public void buyGood(Good good,
